Day-1 test instructions (copy/paste only)

Windows (one-click):
1) Copy/paste this command:
   test_day1.cmd

macOS/Linux (one-click):
1) Copy/paste this command:
   ./test_day1.sh

What the test does:
- Runs the Windows entrypoint to generate output/pose_tracks.json.
- Validates the JSON schema and required fields.
- Prints a success message if everything passes.

Expected success output includes:
- "Wrote pose tracks to" followed by a full path to output/pose_tracks.json
- "Day-1 output validation passed"
- "Day-1 test complete."
